The Origen of OneTimeApp 

OTA #1 is part of the first blueprint designs. There are 4 Originally drew back on 2016 by me Gregory Estevez. 

The Origen of OneTimeApp 

The words “OTA” stands for OneTimeApp, which currently is a mobile app use by hundreds of people in the home care business. 

It is incredible how an idea can come to life. All it requires is persistency and faith. 

1284 x 1284
